<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Thames" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Thames,</orth> the river on which London lies: <cit><quote>to be thrown into the T.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 6</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 6</bibl> <cit><quote>thrown into T.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 6</bibl></cit> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.120" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 120</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.8.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 8, 3</bibl>. <cit><quote>by the T. side,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.3.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 3, 16</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the T. water,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.23" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 23</bibl></cit>.
